snippet.title: Best VGM 2364 - Tales of Symphonia : Dawn of the New World - A Snow Light (Flanoir)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 707 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZJjaiYyES4w

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Tales of Symphonia : Dawn of the New World (2008)
A Snow Light (Flanoir)
Motoi Sakuraba & Shinji Tamura

Art: https://spirit-milla-maxwell.tumblr.com/post/181389290039/merry-christmas-to-all-the-tales-of-fans-and-to
